title: PDF editor (VeryPDF)
description:
VeryPDF PDF Editor is an easy-to-use application designed for users familiar with MicrosoftÃ‚Â® Office and similar applications. 

VeryPDF PDF Editor provides tools to enable you freely write your own comments to the PDF document and share the comments with others. It also provides a very convenient way for you to add contents or change the text or add text in any font you like, especially in filling out electronic forms, correct spelling errors, delete words completely and so on. You can save, move, copy, paste and print the comments and contents. Convert PDF format files to Text files, BMP files, TIFF files, GIF files and so on. Create other format file to PDF file.
